These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, begonia, tulip
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, roller, quad-bike
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, chestnut, lilac, blue
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the person who likes lilac is the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Flower   | sunflower       | bellflower | begonia     | tulip    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | train         | helicopter  | roller    |
| Color           | lilac      | blue       | brown | chestnut |

