.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, magic-tricks, photography, skydiving
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, black, turquise, fuchsia
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, taxi, tram
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby   | camping | magic-tricks   | photography   | skydiving           |
| Color   | black  | fuchsia     | turquise    | brown         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Transport         | bike     | tram  | boat | taxi       |

