.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, brown, white
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, security-guard, electrician, lawyer
City: hamburg, paris, berlin, prague
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, subway, tram, trike
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the lawyer##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person driving the trike is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person who likes white is the security-guard##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the electrician##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the electrician##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Color   | white     | brown      | blood-red | coral      |
| Job           | security-guard       | journalist         | lawyer  | electrician         |
| City         | hamburg | paris | berlin  | prague |
| Transport     | tram       | bike         | trike   | subway        |

