 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the videographer is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the software-developer##1
 9. the freelancer is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
