The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, balloon-flower, begonia
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the pakistani##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the brazilian##1
 6. the brazilian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person who growsbegonia##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the indonesian is on the far right##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the horse##1
12. the pakistani is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Birthday         | february   | december | april    | october  |
