 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the firefighter##1
 2. the cape-cod house is the firefighter##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the security-guard##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person drinking water is the person who likes black##1
11. the person who growstulip is on the left of the wooden house##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| House       | gothic-revival    | palace        | cape-cod  | wooden      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Color         | ivory | blue          | black         | light-blue      |
| Flower   | begonia     | dahlia     | tulip       | iris          |

