.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, game, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo, parkour, handball
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
4 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, mah-jongg, billiard
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the game-smoker is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is the person drinking water##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Cigar         | oliveros | game | aristoff | davidoff  |
| Sport   | parkour    | water-polo     | handball      | skiing |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Game           | scrabble  | billiard       | canasta          | mah-jongg      |

