.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, plum, raspberry, tomato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, 7up
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, amber, red, blue
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rowing, skiing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, disco, dubstep, folk
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
