.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, ebony, light-blue
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, sudoku, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard, social-worker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat, old-henry, vegafina
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, indie, techno, rock
 1. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 3. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the doctor##1
 5. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the fan of indie is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the doctor is the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the fan of techno##1
12. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Color        | chestnut    | light-blue        | orange        | ebony      |
| Hobby       | sudoku       | fishing       | skydiving      | video-games |
| Job         | entrepreneur | social-worker | security-guard | doctor      |
| Cigar         | bongani          | vegafina         | baccarat           | old-henry    |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | indie       | rock     | d&b   |

 